Package: huerd
Title: Pure Minimax Color Palette Optimization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Maximilian", "Scholz", , "dev.scholz@mailbox.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generates scientifically-grounded color palettes using pure minimax 
    optimization to maximize the minimum perceptual distance between colors. Features 
    automatic brightness sorting, comprehensive diagnostic dashboard, and support for 
    fixed brand colors. All optimization performed in the perceptually uniform OKLAB 
    color space with integrated color vision deficiency analysis.
